      "title": "Ranil Resignation: Appointment of Vajira",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "United National Party National List MP Ranil Wickramasinghe has resigned as MP, the Secretary General of Parliament officially announced to the House.",
        "In this case, Vajira Abeywardhana, the party's vice president, was sworn in today (27th morning) in the presence of Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardhana for the vacant National List MP post."
      ],
